Privacy Policy for Navigation Drawer App

Effective date: 20 of march of 2024

Thank you for using Navigation Drawer, a Kotlin app developed to provide a sample of this functionality. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your information when you use our app.

No Data Collection: Navigation Drawer does not collect any personal information or data from its users. We do not gather, store, or process any data about your usage of the app.

Permissions: Navigation Drawer does not require any permissions for its intended functionality, such as accessing location services, camera, or storage.

Third-Party Services: Our app does not contain links to third-party websites or services.

Security: Since Navigation Drawer does not collect any data, there is no data to secure.

Changes to this Privacy Policy: We reserve the right to update or change our Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the updated Privacy Policy on this page.

By using Navigation Drawer, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with these terms, please do not use our app.
